married, was banished in disgrace by Monaco's Prince Rainier after
pictures and videos of him with Houteman at a Riviera villa hit
the mass media.
</P>
<P>
De Lisiecki, who claimed to have spent 70,000 French francs(9,
775 U.S. dollars) on plotting the trap and sold his pictures for
250,000 francs (34,910 dollars), has admitted organizing the trap.
</P>
<P>
Houteman said that she had no idea that she was being used as
part of the trap.
</P>
<P>
