Indian Fishermen who were lodged in various jails in Pakistan.
</P>
<P>
The 41 Pakistani fishermen were released in two batches. On
Monday, 19 Pakistani fishermen, who were washed ashore during a
cyclone last year, were set free. Two days later, 22 Pakistani
fishermen, who had been captured in India's territorial waters,
were released.
</P>
