<HEADLINE> Mongolian People's Revolutionary Party Likely to Win Election </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ULAN BATOR, April 27 (Xinhua) -- The Mongolian People's
Revolutionary Party (MPRP) is likely to win the third election of
the State Great Khural (Mongolia's parliament) scheduled for July
2, according to the latest poll conducted by the unofficial Sant
Maral Foundation.
</P>
<P>
