<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Urges to Improve Social Security System (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Zhu said a social security system that is really separated from
enterprises and institutions should be built up, under which
enterprises and institutions are merely responsible for paying
social security expenses, leaving other things for social security
institutions.
</P>
<P>
The existing methods for re-employment of laid off workers from
state-owned factories should be improved and a reliable and stable
fund-raising system should be set up, he noted.
</P>
<P>
