situation in the aftermath of a civil war in the Democratic
Republic of the Congo (DRC).
</P>
<P>
Japan will disburse 5.5 million U.S. dollars to the office of
the UNHCR as a voluntary contribution to humanitarian assistance.
</P>
<P>
At least 2.5 million dollars would be targeted for the
countries in the sub-Saharan Africa, he said. 
