<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan Vice President George
Saitoti called on African scientists to step up research to stem
the spread of AIDS, malaria and other infectious diseases on the
continent, East African Standard daily reported Thursday.
