<TEXT>
<P>
HELSINKI, April 26 (Xinhua) -- Gert Verheyen scored twice to
lift Belgium a 2-0 victory over Norway in a soccer friendly in
Oslo, Norway on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The Belgian ensured that Norway, which was undefeated on its
Ullevaal Stadium in Oslo between 1991 and 1998, lost its second
home game in a row.
</P>
<P>
