this summer's Euro soccer championships in Arnhem, Netherlands on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Arsenal striker Dennis Bergkamp had at least four chances in
the opening 15 minutes, but failed by a whisker to get any on
target.
</P>
<P>
