teammates joined him. His second in the 36th minute came much
closer after his cross was headed by Everton's Don Hutchison only
to hit the post.
</P>
<P>
The Netherlands' efforts were denied in the second half by
Scotland and Wimbledon goalkeeper Neil Sullivan.
</P>
<P>
Patrick Kluivert, on for the second half only, had his on-
target 65th minute shot blocked by a sprawling Sullivan. His later
effort from a fine cross by Boudewijn Zenden was deflected into
the stand. 
