<HEADLINE> Czechs Republic Waltzes past Israel 4-1 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, April 26 (Xinhua) - Two goals from Pavel Nedved gave
the Czech Republic an easy 4-1 victory over Israel in their
friendly soccer international on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The Lazio midfielder picked up a pass from Pavel Horvath and
opened the scoring in the 14th minute with a right-foot shot that
went in by the right-hand post from 25 meters out.
</P>
<P>
