collected a pass from Radek Bejbl, cracked in a low shot from the
edge of the box, scoring his 13th goal in 13 matches for the
national team.
</P>
<P>
Nedved added his second from an 18-meter free kick after 57
minutes before Israel scored nine minutes from time when Ilan
Bachar found the unmarked Eyal Berkoviz who scored.
</P>
<P>
Rene Wagner added the fourth Czech goal in the last minute.
